# AI Cars Detection

Analyzes a picture of a highway, intersection, or traffic light stop and detects the cars on the road(s).  It can be useful when determining a efficient way to clear up traffic on the roads. \>


## The Algorithm

Detectnet is used from the Jetson-Inference library of tools to categorize what is in the picture. It includes a picture of your choice from the Internet that pertains to cars on the road. 


## Running this project

1. cd Cars\_AI\_Project  
2. wget (link from the internet of a picture pertaining to cars on a road)  
3. detectnet.py “name of picture” new\_name
